Implementation TODO Plan – Prime Site (Option A: Eleventy)

Decision
- Adopt Eleventy (11ty) + Nunjucks + Tailwind CDN to centralize facts with minimal rewrite. Keep current HTML structure where possible.

Phase 0 — Baseline & Canonical Facts
- Define canonical values: 700,000 THB (+VAT), 150 rounds/year, 2 seats, 3 guests/seat (max 6 if both present), 48h cancel, 5,000 THB transfer.
- Domains/emails: primethailand.golf; concierge@primethailand.golf; privacy@primethailand.golf.
- Identify public vs internal pages (internal: UAT, Concierge Manual, Launch Plan/Checklist, Outreach, Finance); mark `noindex` later.
- Grep drift now: `rg -nE '(144|949,000|950,000|primegolf\\.co|Founders)' HTML_DRAFTS *.html`.

Phase 1 — 11ty Scaffold
- Add structure:
  site/.eleventy.js
  site/_data/site.json (single source of truth)
  site/_includes/{layout.njk,header.njk,footer.njk,glance-cards.njk}
  site/pages/ (public), site/internal/ (noindex), site/legal/, site/member/, site/assets/
- Commands:
  npm init -y && npm i @11ty/eleventy
  npx eleventy --serve (outputs to site/_site by default)

Phase 2 — Single Source of Truth (site/_data/site.json)
- Example shape:
  {
    "brand": { "name": "Prime", "company": "Prime Corporate Golf Club" },
    "domain": "primethailand.golf",
    "contact": { "concierge": "concierge@primethailand.golf", "privacy": "privacy@primethailand.golf" },
    "membership": { "priceTHB": 700000, "rounds": 150, "seats": 2, "guestsPerSeat": 3, "transferFeeTHB": 5000, "cancelHrs": 48 },
    "policy": { "privacyLastUpdated": "2025-10-20" }
  }

Phase 3 — Page Migration (map → convert → bind data)
- landing.html → site/pages/index.njk (marketing hero, At‑a‑Glance via `site.membership`).
- HTML_DRAFTS/Pricing & Terms.html AND HTML_DRAFTS/Prime Corporate Golf Club | Pricing & Terms.html → site/pages/pricing-terms.njk (canonical). Replace 949k/tiers with 700k single plan; use accordion partial.
- HTML_DRAFTS/prime booklet V3.html + V4.html → site/member/booklet.njk (unify; 144→150; 2+6 guest policy).
- HTML_DRAFTS/Member Welcome Package.html → site/member/welcome-package.njk (update emails/domain).
- HTML_DRAFTS/Privacy Policy.html → site/legal/privacy.njk (PDPA; update contacts; date from `policy`).
- HTML_DRAFTS/E-Signature Agreement.html → site/legal/agreement.njk (144→150; fee 700k; domain/emails).
- HTML_DRAFTS/UAT Dashboard.html → site/internal/uat.njk (progress bars/tables; `noindex`).
- HTML_DRAFTS/Concierge Manual.html → site/internal/concierge-manual.njk (`noindex`).
- HTML_DRAFTS/Launch Checklist.html → site/internal/launch-checklist.njk (`noindex`).
- HTML_DRAFTS/Go-to-Market Launch Plan Dashboard.html → site/internal/launch-plan.njk (`noindex`).
- HTML_DRAFTS/Target Company Outreach Dashboard.html → site/internal/outreach.njk (`noindex`).
- HTML_DRAFTS/Branded Merchandise Showcase.html → site/pages/merchandise.njk.
- HTML_DRAFTS/Sales Presentation.html + Pricing & Incentives.html → remove tiered tables; reflect single plan (either merge into pricing or stage as archived internal).

Phase 4 — Shared Partials & Styling
- Extract header/footer; add Tailwind CDN in layout.njk head.
- Create glance-cards.njk bound to `site.membership` (80+ courses text remains as copy).
- Mark internal pages with `<meta name="robots" content="noindex,nofollow">`.

Phase 5 — QA & Guardrails
- Serve locally: `npx eleventy --serve`; verify all routes.
- Validate markup: `npx html-validate site/_site/**/*.html` (if installed) or W3C validator.
- Broken links: `npx linkinator http://localhost:8080`.
- Lighthouse on key pages (pricing, privacy, booklet).
- Drift checks (must be zero matches):
  rg -nE '(144|949,000|950,000|primegolf\\.co|Founders)' site/**/*.njk

Phase 6 — Deploy
- Choose host (Cloudflare Pages/Netlify). Build command: `npx eleventy`. Publish `site/_site/`.
- Add sitemap.xml, robots.txt (block `/internal/`). Set canonical domain to https://primethailand.golf.

Acceptance Criteria
- All numeric facts render from `site/_data/site.json`.
- No occurrences of 144/949k/950k/primegolf.co/Founders in generated HTML.
- Internal pages are reachable but `noindex` and off primary nav.
- Pricing, Terms, Privacy, Agreement, Booklet, Welcome Package align on plan details.

Notes
- Do not delete original HTML_DRAFTS during migration; keep as reference until sign‑off.
- If Eleventy is later replaced by Astro, reuse the same data model and component mapping from chatgpt_review.md.
